in terms i mean there are words in pali which separate fear and anxiety but for our purposes we can put them all into one just this word fear um the way we act the way we experience fear is is a sudden jolt of a bad energy in the body and it tends to go away so if you step out on the road and a car just misses you you get that fright whereas

